reviewText: My jaw dropped when I saw this DVD available on Amazon. The Daughters of Joshua Cabe has NEVER been available in ANY way whatsoever. This movie along with The Young Pioneers were both ABC Movies of the Week.Watching them really bought back wonderful memories.I have yet to watch the other movies that are on these 2 discs, but I will watch them soon.If you have been as anxious as I have to find the 2 movies I mentioned then don't hesitate to get this DVD.So happy to finally have these movies.I'm hoping that I start to see more movies of the week available on Amazon.Especially THE FEMINIST & THE FUZZ with Barbara Eden.
summary: AT LAST!!!! THE DAUGHTERS OF JOSHUA CABE & YOUNG PIONEERS!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!

reviewText: It was interesting to watch these different kinds of movies. Loved to see how the importance the bible is displayed. The picture quality of the older movies is pretty bad at times. Nevertheless it is great to see the beauty of unspoiled nature. "Nothing to good for a cowboy" it not really a movie for children, I did enjoy watching how Gloria and Rich stand up for one another. Yes and how Rich respects the importance of marriage.
